OL,3,CNatalie McNally family describe her as
OL,4,C'inspirational person'
OL,6,FThe family of Natalie McNally have
OL,7,Fdescribed her as an "inspirational
OL,8,Fperson" after her partner was found
OL,9,Fguilty of her murder.
OL,11,FMs McNally was 15 weeks pregnant when
OL,12,Fshe was beaten and stabbed at her home
OL,13,Fin Lurgan on December 18 2022.
OL,15,FOn Monday, a jury found Stephen
OL,16,FMcCullagh guilty of murdering the 32-
OL,17,Fyear-old.
OL,19,FMs McNally's brothers, Niall and
OL,20,FDeclan McNally, spoke outside Belfast
OL,21,FCrown Court after the verdict.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
