OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774343101
OL,3,CNatalie McNally family describe her as
OL,4,C'inspirational person'
OL,6,FDeclan McNally said: "As Natalie
OL,7,Freceives justice today, our hearts go
OL,8,Fout to all the victims of violence
OL,9,Fagainst women and girls.
OL,11,F"Our hope is that all the victims and
OL,12,Ffamilies get their day in court and
OL,13,Fthe justice they deserve.
OL,15,F"Violence against women and girls is
OL,16,Fthe shame of our society and we must
OL,17,Fdo everything possible to end it."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774343101
OL,3,CNatalie McNally family describe her as
OL,4,C'inspirational person'
OL,6,FHe added: "Natalie, you were an
OL,7,Finspirational person. Having you in
OL,8,Four lives was the greatest joy we will
OL,9,Fever have.
OL,11,F"You would have been an amazing mother
OL,12,Fto baby Dean and we will love you
OL,13,Fforever and hope you can now rest
OL,14,Feasy."
OL,16,F"Declan also paid tribute to his
OL,17,Fmother and father and said: "Over the
OL,18,Flast three-and-a-half years, I don't
OL,19,Fknow how they have done it.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1774343101
OL,3,CNatalie McNally family describe her as
OL,4,C'inspirational person'
OL,6,F"They are the most amazing people.
OL,7,FThey have the biggest strength you
OL,8,Fcould ever think of and how they have
OL,9,Fheld this all together, they are
OL,10,Famazing and we love you very much."
OL,12,FNiall McNally also spoke and thanked
OL,13,Fthe PSNI, the PPS and the prosecution
OL,14,Fbarristers for "working so hard on the
OL,15,Fcase" and Victim Support.
OL,17,FHe also thanked Mr Justice Kinney for
OL,18,F"presiding over a fair trial" and to
OL,19,Fthe jury "for their verdict today."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
