OL,3,CNatalie McNally family describe her as
OL,4,C'inspirational person'
OL,6,FIn addition, Declan praised the wider
OL,7,Ffamily and friends for their support,
OL,8,Fas well as the communities in Lurgan
OL,9,Fand beyond.
OL,11,FHe said: "Without their support we
OL,12,Fwould not got through this most
OL,13,Fdifficult time in our lives."
